beer.beer_name: Wolf & Fox Slovenian Hopped Pale Ale
beer.beer_description:
For this Pale Ale, two Slovenian Hops come together - Styrian Wolf and Styrian Fox! The aroma is fruity, herbal, and floral, before a clean body of fruits from blackberry to mango.

A howling scream.
